title: Mothra 3: Invasion of King Ghidorah/Rebirth of Mothra 3
description: This is an English fansubbed AVI of Mothra 3: Invasion of King Ghidorah.  This movie was dubbed by Sony, but never released in the U.S., outside of Sci-Fi channel.  The English subtitles do not obscure any of the video, as it is a widescreen movie.  The visual quality is fair, but nowhere near as good as it could have been, due to compression.  The original version of this torrent was first uploaded on Demonoid, and because of this, I have taken the liberty of including the Demonoid tracker along with TPB&#039;s on its list.
